INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (41, 1, '2010-05-15 19:52:47', '2010-05-15 18:52:47', '<img src="/art/pirate-thumb.jpg" alt="Fearless" />\r\n\r\nThis was an entry I did for <a href="http://www.illustrationfriday.com" target="_blank">Illustration Friday</a>.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img src="/art/pirate-p.jpg" alt="Fearless" />\r\n\r\nThe word for the week was Fearless so I chose to draw a Pirate as they are reckless and daring. I based the Pirate on Captain Blackbeard as he is one of the most notorious. I also used part of this illustration for my CV which can be downloaded from the "About" page.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<img src="/art/pirate-close1.jpg" alt="Fearless - Close up" /><br><br>\r\n<img src="/art/pirate-close2.jpg" alt="Fearless - Close up"><br><br>\r\n\r\nSketched in pencil, inked and coloured in Photoshop.', 'Fearless', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'fearless', '', '', '2010-06-08 20:42:57', '2010-06-08 19:42:57', '', 0, 'http://old.cazlock.com/?p=41', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (43, 1, '2010-05-16 22:47:22', '2010-05-16 21:47:22', '<img src="/art/whale-thumb.jpg" alt="Serene" />\r\n\r\nThis illustration was done to go along side my Pirate piece <a href="http://www.cazlock.com/2010/05/fearless/">"Fearless"</a>.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img src="/art/whale-colour-p.jpg" alt="Serene" />\r\n\r\nThey were originally going to be the same piece for a submission to Illustration Friday for the word the Fearless. I decided though that they didn''t work well together for the theme. Instead I used this Illustration a long side "Fearless" on my CV, which can be downloaded through the About Page. I love this as much as the Pirate though so I made this a colour piece to go alongside the other.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<img src="/art/whale-close1.jpg" alt="Serene - Close up" /><br><br>\r\n<img src="/art/whale-close2.jpg" alt="Serene - Close up"><br><br>\r\n\r\nSketched in pencil, inked and coloured in Photoshop.', 'Serene', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'serene', '', '', '2010-06-23 22:48:47', '2010-06-23 21:48:47', '', 0, 'http://old.cazlock.com/?p=43', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (45, 1, '2010-07-18 22:04:09', '2010-07-18 21:04:09', '<img src="/art/okami-thumb.jpg" alt="Amaterasu" />\r\n\r\nThis fan art of Amaterasu from Okami has a twist as I decided to design her in as a human rather than how she appears in the game; as a White Wolf.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img src="/art/okami.jpg" alt="Amaterasu" /><br>\r\n\r\nI wanted to keep certain traits that Amaterasu has from the game so I made her hair a similar colour and kept the tattoo''s from her body. Her Kimono design has Sakura, Cherry Blossom, on it as they are featured heavily in the game. The flower on her belt, or Obi, is from one of the Celestial Brush Techniques that Amaterasu uses.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<img src="/art/okami-close.jpg" alt="Close up" /><br><br>\r\n<img src="/art/okami-close1.jpg" alt="Close up" /><br>\r\n\r\nSketched in pencil, inked and coloured in Photoshop.<br>\r\nTextures can be found <a href="http://browse.deviantart.com/?qh=&amp;section=&amp;global=1&amp;q=wahu#/d1ozb0m" target="_blank">here</a>.<br>\r\nThe logo and background images I picked up from when the Okami Contest was held on Deviant Art many moons ago. So thanks to Clover/Capcom and Deviant Art for supplying them.', 'Amaterasu - Human Form', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'amaterasu-human-form', '', '', '2010-07-18 22:08:53', '2010-07-18 21:08:53', '', 0, 'http://old.cazlock.com/?p=45', 0, 'post', '', 0);
